Package org.eclipse.mosaic.fed.sumo.ambassador

package org.eclipse.mosaic.fed.sumo.ambassador
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    LibSumoAmbassador
    Implementation of the bridge between MOSAIC and SUMO using the native libsumojni binding provided with SUMO.
    SumoAmbassador
    Implementation of a AbstractFederateAmbassador for the traffic simulator SUMO.
    SumoInfrastructureHandler
    All the ambassador's logic which takes care of infrastructure elements (variable traffic signs, detectors).
    SumoPersonsHandler
    All the ambassador's logic which takes care of persons/agents.
    SumoRoutesHandler
    All the ambassador's logic which takes care of routes.
    SumoTrafficLightsHandler
    All the ambassador's logic which takes care of traffic lights.
    SumoVehicleActionsHandler
    All the ambassador's logic which takes care of actions of vehicles, such as stopping or lane changing.
    SumoVehiclesHandler
    All the ambassador's logic which takes care of managing vehicles, such as adding, subscribing, deleting.
